    <li><strong>Anthropic accuses Chinese labs of AI distillation</strong>: Anthropic claims DeepSeek, Moonshot, and MiniMax executed "industrial-scale" campaigns to siphon Claude’s proprietary reasoning capabilities. Over 16 million exchanges were identified, potentially enabling the bypass of US export controls. <a href="https://cyberscoop.com/anthropic-accuses-chinese-labs-ai-distillation-cyber-risk/" target="_blank">More info</a></li>
  </ul>

